OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat Nottingham University Hospitals
OL,8,FTrust because of what it says are
OL,9,Fsustained pressures across its
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FThe Trust says the emergency
OL,13,Fdepartment at the Queen's Medical
OL,14,FCentre in Nottingham is particularly
OL,15,Faffected, and people should only go in
OL,16,Fan emergency.
OL,18,FThe critical incident was called just
OL,19,Fafter 4pm on Tuesday 4 November, after
OL,20,F24 ambulances were reportedly waiting
OL,21,Foutside the QMC's emergency department.
