OL,3,CCritical incident declared at
OL,4,CNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,6,FThe Trust says it's due to a
OL,7,Fcombination of sustained demand,
OL,8,Fstaffing issues and challenges around
OL,9,Fstaffing.
OL,11,FAnyone with a planned appointment is
OL,12,Fbeing advised to continue to attend
OL,13,Funless told otherwise.
OL,15,FThe Chief Operating Officer at NUH,
OL,16,FAndrew Hall, said: "Our staff are
OL,17,Fworking tirelessly to care for
OL,18,Fpatients, but the pressure on our
OL,19,Fservices is causing very long waits
OL,20,Fand this is causing overcrowding in
OL,21,Four ED.
