OL,6,F"We know how frustrating this will be
OL,7,Fto people waiting in the department.
OL,8,FOur staff are working as hard as they
OL,9,Fpossibly can to get to them as soon as
OL,10,Fpossible. Unfortunately, some of our
OL,11,Fcolleagues have experienced abuse from
OL,12,Fpeople waiting to be treated and we
OL,13,Fask that they are treated with
OL,14,Fkindness and respect.
OL,16,F"The public can help us by only
OL,17,Fattending ED in an emergency and
OL,18,Fcarefully considering other options,
OL,19,Fsuch as calling NHS111, speaking to a
OL,20,FGP and visiting a local pharmacy.
