OL,6,F"Our emergency services remain open
OL,7,Fand the public should continue to come
OL,8,Fforward as normal in emergency and
OL,9,Flife-threatening cases - when someone
OL,10,Fis seriously ill or injured, or their
OL,11,Flife is at risk. Our aim is to
OL,12,Fprioritise patients with the highest
OL,13,Flevel of need and ensure that we
OL,14,Fcontinue to manage emergency care."
